condition_query:
FROM KafkaConsumerLag
SELECT max(secondsLag)
WHERE topic = 'cell_partial_aggregates'
  AND group = 'daqs-mirror-pae'
  AND cluster = 'staging.stg-itchy-salt'

policy_name: UDS - Staging - QA cells - Lag - Non-Pageable - stg-itchy-salt
condition_name: WARNING Staging Mirror Maker Lag in stg-itchy-salt
condition_query:
FROM KafkaConsumerLag
SELECT max(secondsLag)
WHERE topic in ('daqs_registered_queries')
  AND group LIKE '%mirror%'
  AND group NOT LIKE '%msk-'
  AND (
    cluster = 'staging.stg-itchy-salt'
    OR group like '%stg-itchy-salt%'
  )
  AND secondsLag != 28800
  FACET topic, group, cluster

policy_name: UDS - Staging - TDM - Kafka Producer Quotas - Non-Pageable - stg-itchy-salt
condition_name: WARNING Staging Producer Near Quota in stg-itchy-salt
condition_query:
FROM KafkaClientStats
SELECT max(produceByteRateSec/produceQuotaBytePerSec) * 100
WHERE cluster like 'stg-itchy-salt%'
  AND produceQuotaBytePerSec > 0
  AND clientId in ('producer.wam-snapshots.window-aggregation-merger.aggregation-pipeline','producer.wam-results.window-aggregation-merger.aggregation-pipeline','producer.mirror-pae.daqs','producer.simple-decider.daqs')
FACET clientId

condition_name: WARNING Staging Producer Throttled in stg-itchy-salt

FROM KafkaClientStats
SELECT max(produceThrottleTimeMs)
WHERE cluster like 'stg-itchy-salt%'
  AND clientId in ('producer.wam-snapshots.window-aggregation-merger.aggregation-pipeline','producer.wam-results.window-aggregation-merger.aggregation-pipeline','producer.mirror-pae.daqs','producer.simple-decider.daqs')
FACET clientId

condition_name: Topic is not being consumed - metric_cardinality_approximations
condition_query:
SELECT IFTHEN(max(percentOfCells) >= 1 OR max(percentOfCells) < 0.1, 1) OR 0
FROM (
  FROM KafkaConsumerLag SELECT (
      filter(uniqueCount(cell), WHERE topic = 'metric_cardinality_approximations' AND group LIKE '%mirror%')
    / filter(uniqueCount(cell), WHERE topic = 'short_term_metric_data_points')
  ) AS 'percentOfCells'
  WHERE environment LIKE 'staging%'
  AND cell NOT IN ('marathon', 'us-quixotic-task', 'us-jurassic-dust', 'us-crabby-apple') AND cell NOT IN ('stg-single-tooth', 'stg-bark-meow')
  AND ((topic = 'metric_cardinality_approximations' AND group LIKE '%mirror%')
    OR (topic = 'short_term_metric_data_points'))
  FACET environment
)

FROM KafkaConsumerLag
SELECT (latest(retentionMs)/1000) - max(secondsLag)
WHERE latestConsumedOffset != -1
AND clientId NOT LIKE '%kynapses'
AND topic = 'metric_cardinality_approximations'
AND cluster like 'staging.%' AND clusterName NOT IN ('stg-single-tooth', 'stg-bark-meow') AND group NOT LIKE '%stg-single-tooth%' AND group NOT LIKE '%stg-bark-meow%'
AND group LIKE '%mirror%'
WHERE (group NOT LIKE '%mirror-msk%' OR group NOT LIKE '%test%') AND group != 'open_instrumentation_metadata_service' 
FACET cluster

FROM KafkaConsumerLag SELECT max(secondsLag) WHERE topic = 'metric_cardinality_approximations' AND group like '%mirror%' AND cluster like 'staging.%' AND clusterName NOT IN ('stg-single-tooth', 'stg-bark-meow') AND group NOT LIKE '%stg-single-tooth%' AND group NOT LIKE '%stg-bark-meow%'  WHERE (group NOT LIKE '%mirror-msk%' OR group NOT LIKE '%test%') AND group != 'open_instrumentation_metadata_service'  FACET cluster, topic, group

policy_name: UDS - Staging - TI/MTS cells - Lag - Non-Pageable - stg-sea-dragon
condition_query:
FROM KafkaConsumerLag
SELECT max(secondsLag)
WHERE topic IN ('matched_analytic_events', 'matched_event_batches')
  AND group IN ('partial_aggregation_windower_matched_events', 'partial_aggregation_windower_matched_event_batches')
  AND cluster = 'staging.stg-sea-dragon'
FACET topic

policy_name: UDS - Staging - TI/MTS cells - Lag - Non-Pageable - stg-sea-dragon
condition_name: WARNING Staging Mirror Maker Lag in stg-sea-dragon
condition_query:
FROM KafkaConsumerLag
SELECT max(secondsLag)
WHERE topic in ('daqs_registered_queries','stream_rules','event_drop_rules','shuffle_sharding_metadata')
  AND group LIKE '%mirror%'
  AND group NOT LIKE '%msk-'
  AND (
    cluster = 'staging.stg-sea-dragon'
    OR group like '%stg-sea-dragon%'
  )
  AND secondsLag != 28800
  FACET topic, group, cluster

policy_name: UDS - Staging - TI/MTS cells - Lag - Non-Pageable - stg-sea-dragon
condition_name: WARNING Staging Stand Alone Shuffle Sharder lag
condition_query:
FROM KafkaConsumerLag
SELECT max(secondsLag)
WHERE topic = 'unsharded_partial_aggregates'
  AND group = 'partial-aggregate-shuffle-sharder'
  AND cluster = 'staging.stg-sea-dragon'
  AND cluster NOT LIKE 'staging.test-%'
FACET cluster

condition_name: PIE Base images: Security violation on hardened images
condition_query: SELECT count(*) FROM ContainerScan WHERE ScanStatus = 'ScanDirty' AND Scanner !='Dockle' AND Source != 'Local' AND ContainerImage IN ('cf-registry.nr-ops.net/newrelic/base-ubuntu:20.04', 'cf-registry.nr-ops.net/newrelic/base-alpine:3.14')

condition_name: PIE Container Security Scans: Trivy percentage of unknown errors
condition_query: SELECT percentage(count(*), WHERE ScanStatus ='ScanError' AND ScanError NOT LIKE 'error: image not reachable%') FROM ContainerScan WHERE Scanner='Trivy' AND Source != 'Local' AND ScanStatus != 'ControlFailed'

condition_name: PIE Container Security Scans: Dockle percentage of scan errors
condition_query: SELECT percentage(count(*), WHERE ScanStatus ='ScanError') FROM ContainerScan WHERE Scanner='Dockle' AND Source != 'Local' AND ScanStatus != 'ControlFailed'

condition_name: PIE Container Security Scans: ContainerScan percentage of image non reachable errors
condition_query: SELECT percentage(count(*), WHERE ScanStatus ='ScanError' AND ScanError LIKE 'error: image not reachable%') FROM ContainerScan WHERE Scanner='Trivy' AND Source != 'Local' AND ScanStatus != 'ControlFailed'
SELECT average(host.disk.usedPercent) as 'Storage Usage' FROM Metric WHERE entity.guid IN ('MXxJTkZSQXxOQXwzMzI3NjEyMzAxOTAyMDE2NDgy') FACET entity.name

SELECT uniqueCount(processId) FROM ProcessSample WHERE (`operatingSystem` = 'linux' AND `processDisplayName` IN ('httpd', 'java', 'sendmail', 'smtp', 'smtpd', 'crond', 'ntpd', 'mysqld')) FACET processDisplayName
select filter(count(*), where privateLocation IS false) from Synthetics

condition_name: Production job throughput by job type (TF)
condition_query: SELECT uniqueCount(jobId) from Synthetics where isPrivateLocation is false and runtimeVersion != 'unknown' facet jobType
SELECT percentile(jobDuration-executionDuration, 99)/1000/60 from Synthetics where privateLocation is false AND runtimeVersion != 'unknown' AND location NOT LIKE 'LINODE%' FACET location

condition_name: Production Active Public Minion Count by Location (TF)
condition_query: SELECT uniqueCount(minionId) FROM Synthetics WHERE minionBuildNumber = 'unknown' AND isPrivateLocation is false facet location
SELECT count(jobId) from Synthetics WHERE privateLocation is true
SELECT uniqueCount(minionId) FROM SyntheticsMinion WHERE minionLocationIsPrivate is false FACET minionPhysicalLocation
SELECT percentage(count(*), where error like 'Internal Engine%') FROM Synthetics where secureCredentialCount > 0 and privateLocation is false

condition_name: Prod PrivateLocationStatus account processing timer events count (TF)
condition_query: SELECT count(*) FROM SyntheticsMetrics WHERE metricName LIKE 'PrivateLocationStatusPublishService.accountProcessingTimer'
SELECT filter(count(*), where secureCredentialCount > 0) FROM Synthetics
SELECT uniqueCount(minionId) FROM SyntheticsMinion WHERE minionLocationIsPrivate is true

condition_name: Production: Job Soft Failures High By Location (TF)

condition_name: Multiple OOM kills detected for workflow-processing in us-staging
condition_query:
FROM K8sContainerSample
SELECT count(*)
WHERE reason = 'OOMKilled'
  AND namespace = 'uefa'
  AND containerName = 'workflow-processing'
  AND label.environment = 'us-staging'
FACET clusterName, podName

condition_name: CPU Utilization is high for workflow-processing in us-staging
condition_query:
FROM K8sContainerSample
SELECT average(cpuUsedCores)/max(cpuRequestedCores) * 100 AS utilizedPercent
WHERE namespace = 'uefa'
  AND containerName = 'workflow-processing'
  AND label.environment = 'us-staging'
FACET clusterName, podName

condition_name: workflow-processing pods are missing in deployment in us-staging
condition_query:
FROM K8sDeploymentSample
SELECT min(podsDesired-podsAvailable)
WHERE namespace = 'uefa'
  AND deploymentName = 'workflow-processing'
  AND label.environment = 'us-staging'
FACET clusterName, deploymentName

condition_name: Multiple pod failures detected for workflow-processing in us-staging
condition_query:
FROM K8sPodSample
SELECT count(*)
WHERE status = 'Failed'
  AND reason != 'Evicted'
  AND createdKind != 'Job'
  AND namespace = 'uefa'
  AND deploymentName = 'workflow-processing'
  AND label.environment = 'us-staging'
FACET clusterName, podName

condition_name: workflow-processing pod is not ready in us-staging

FROM K8sContainerSample

FACET clusterName, podName

condition_name: CPU Throttled percentage is high for workflow-processing in us-staging

policy_name: UDS - Staging - TDM - Kafka Producer Quotas - Non-Pageable - stg-ultimate-jam
condition_name: WARNING Staging Producer Near Quota in stg-ultimate-jam
condition_query:
FROM KafkaClientStats
SELECT max(produceByteRateSec/produceQuotaBytePerSec) * 100
WHERE cluster like 'stg-ultimate-jam%'
  AND produceQuotaBytePerSec > 0
  AND clientId in ('producer.wam-snapshots.window-aggregation-merger.aggregation-pipeline','producer.wam-results.window-aggregation-merger.aggregation-pipeline','producer.mirror-pae.daqs')
FACET clientId

policy_name: UDS - Staging - TDM - Kafka Producer Quotas - Non-Pageable - stg-ultimate-jam
condition_name: WARNING Staging Producer Throttled in stg-ultimate-jam
condition_query:
FROM KafkaClientStats
SELECT max(produceThrottleTimeMs)
WHERE cluster like 'stg-ultimate-jam%'
  AND clientId in ('producer.wam-snapshots.window-aggregation-merger.aggregation-pipeline','producer.wam-results.window-aggregation-merger.aggregation-pipeline','producer.mirror-pae.daqs')
FACET clientId

policy_name: UDS - Staging - QA cells - Retention - Non-Pageable - stg-ultimate-jam

FROM KafkaBrokerTopicStats
SELECT max(maxPartitionSizeBytes)/max(retentionBytes)
WHERE cluster like 'stg-ultimate-jam%'
  AND topic in ('cell_partial_aggregates','partially_aggregated_events','undecided_daqs_results')
facet topic

policy_name: UDS - Staging - QA cells - Lag - Non-Pageable - stg-ultimate-jam

WHERE topic = 'cell_partial_aggregates'

policy_name: UDS - Staging - QA cells - Lag - Non-Pageable - stg-ultimate-jam
condition_name: WARNING Staging Window Aggregation Merger lag in stg-ultimate-jam

FROM KafkaConsumerLag

  AND cluster = 'staging.stg-ultimate-jam'

policy_name: UDS - Staging - QA cells - Lag - Non-Pageable - stg-ultimate-jam
